{"tid":8181,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以教中五數學","createTime":"2016-11-28T08:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T15:53:28.000Z","uid":9155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad1c9ead47d6c4b97cb7ba152b9f6d1e63cc546","tid":8181,"uid":9155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"數學一科拉低曬平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前唔夠努力 而家點做數都覺得好吃力<br />\n希望巴打除左屌醒我之外教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a39b489443c9f2a33f5f415835fc4abc90925ba","tid":8181,"uid":1742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"有無讀M1 M2?"},{"pid":"b75d71a80cef918f3397cc89b91f1fcd29d25cbe","tid":8181,"uid":12521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:09:22.000Z","msg":"香港補習良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己YouTube"},{"pid":"01c3ac10df85d9bbd4205e1a9ce7bf70884982ad","tid":8181,"uid":14094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"652b2899ac40157cdeeb303b172a28e4ec8cd2c6","tid":8181,"uid":17163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"可以幫下手<br />\n<br />\n利申: A + 大學讀數"},{"pid":"f1c98624f405b65646db1ccc8880a59e8be5dbe6","tid":8181,"uid":9155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾你老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32ed8d509946d4d5afb6dea41fe7c43316f05d3","tid":8181,"uid":9155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無讀M1 M2?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d3f857103ae26c09dd94432d8ac0e1326c9421","tid"